FBIS3-55486 "drsov006_s_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-006 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Jan 1994 Georgia To Be Buried in Chechnya LD1001150794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1349 GMT 10 Jan 94 LD1001150794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Groznyy, 10 Dec (CHECHENPRESS-TASS) -- The body of Georgian ex-president Zviad Gamsakhurdia will be buried in Chechnya, Shamsuddin Yusef, the Chechen Republic's foreign minister announced at a briefing in Groznyy today. He added that this was in accordance with the wishes of Gamsakhurdia's family. According to Shamsuddin Yusef, necessary permission for burying the ex-president in Chechnya has been received from the Georgian leadership.
